OL,7,FBritish Steel has said it will close
OL,8,Fcoke ovens at its Scunthorpe plant
OL,9,Fthreatening up to 260 jobs.
OL,11,FThe Chinese-owned steelmaker said the
OL,12,Fmove was necessary because steelmaking
OL,13,Fin Britain was "uncompetitive" with
OL,14,Fhigh energy, carbon and labour costs.
OL,16,FThe company said "decisive action" was
OL,17,Fneeded because of an "unprecedented
OL,18,Frise" in its energy and carbon bills
OL,19,Fwhich increased by #190m last year.
OL,3,CBritish Steel: Hundreds of jobs axed as
OL,4,CChinese owners say UK is
OL,5,C'uncompetitive'
